OL,3,CWatch the moment north Wales driver
OL,4,Crams car in road rage incident
OL,6,FA man has received a suspended prison
OL,7,Fsentence and been banned from driving
OL,8,Fafter ramming another car in a road
OL,9,Frage incident on the A55 last year.
OL,11,FPaul Woodward, 55 of Prestatyn,
OL,12,Fappeared at Caernarfon Crown Court
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident on the
OL,14,Feastbound carriageway of Rhuallt Hill
OL,15,Fon 15 September 2023.
