OL,3,CWatch the moment north Wales driver
OL,4,Crams car in road rage incident
OL,6,FWoodward claimed the other motorist,
OL,7,Fwho had tried to overtake him, was at
OL,8,Ffault for the collision but CCTV
OL,9,Ffootage was shown to the court which
OL,10,Fshowed Woodward, driving a Citroen
OL,11,FBerlingo van, clipping the rear of a
OL,12,Fsilver VW Golf.
OL,14,FThe collision caused the VW to spin on
OL,15,Fthe carriageway while traffic speed
OL,16,Faround it.
OL,18,FNobody was seriously injured during
OL,19,Fthe incident.
