OL,3,CWatch the moment north Wales driver
OL,4,Crams car in road rage incident
OL,6,FNorth Wales Police were called to the
OL,7,Fcollision which happened shortly after
OL,8,F4:30pm and Woodward was arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving.
OL,11,FHe was later charged and convicted of
OL,12,Fdangerous driving at trial.
OL,14,FPC Haydn Roberts-Powell from North
OL,15,FWales Police's Roads Crime Unit
OL,16,Fwelcomed the sentence.
OL,18,FHe said: "Paul Woodward's actions that
OL,19,Fday were highly dangerous and it is a
OL,20,Fmiracle that no-one, including other
OL,21,Fpassing motorists, were seriously hurt.
