OL,3,CWatch the moment north Wales driver
OL,4,Crams car in road rage incident
OL,6,F"It is clear that this was fuelled by
OL,7,Froad rage which is clearly
OL,8,Funacceptable. We will actively target
OL,9,Fthose individuals that feel they can
OL,10,Fdrive and act in this way."
OL,12,FWoodward was sentenced to 15 months in
OL,13,Fprison ` suspended for 18 months. He
OL,14,Fwas ordered to carry out 20 days
OL,15,Frehabilitation work and 150 hours of
OL,16,Funpaid work.
OL,18,FHe was also disqualified from driving
OL,19,Ffor 18 months and has to pay a
OL,20,Fstatutory surcharge.
